    <h1>Implicit Local Intent</h1>
    <p class="description">When Google recognizes a query requires local results <strong>even though the searcher included no location</strong>. Searches like "pizza delivery" or "dentist" trigger the Local Pack without any city name — because Google knows the intent is inherently local.</p>
